casebody.data:
Sheila H. KURTZ, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
Helen GELLER, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-1781 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. SEPTEMBER 26, 2017 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and SUAREZ and SALTER, JJ., concur.

Upon the Court's own motion, it is ordered that this appeal from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida is dismissed for failure to comply with this Court's order dated August 21, 2017, and with the Florida Rules of Appellate Procedure.
